{"id": 1773, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些判断一个演员演技的心得？", "description": "演技好不好，我一看就知道。", "record_count": 3906, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170629165930cMpASiIXd8NWxYBH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-20T03:00:52Z", "options": [{"id": 223744, "content": "看眼神就知道他的心情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956977}, {"id": 224000, "content": "共鸣，好演员扮演的角色会让你对这个角色认同。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518460}, {"id": 223745, "content": "评论这个演员的不是什么有礼貌，学霸这类和演技无关的形容词", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79433}, {"id": 224257, "content": "郑爽、杨幂、宋茜、唐嫣不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085158}, {"id": 223746, "content": "看眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988192}, {"id": 224770, "content": "话剧？有演话剧经验的演员底子都该过硬吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285511}, {"id": 226818, "content": "极端情绪的表演，愤怒，痛苦，无奈等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954495}, {"id": 223747, "content": "感情流露眼神最为重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083384}, {"id": 224003, "content": "【假戏真做】", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 224771, "content": "过去的情景喜剧演员们都挺棒的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285511}, {"id": 223748, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006815}, {"id": 224004, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522195}, {"id": 223749, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067047}, {"id": 224005, "content": "演什么是什么，完全不留自己和之前角色的影子；代入感极强，总会让人发出“啊，这个人物就应该是这样”的类似感叹；一个人完全可以撑起一部戏，可以拯救一部戏，甚至成为了看这部戏唯一的理由。详情可参见俞承豪的《君主 假面的主人》", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082442}, {"id": 223750, "content": "张鲁一张鲁一张鲁一", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830536}, {"id": 224006, "content": "看得尴不尴尬，有没有让我浑身不自在", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079679}, {"id": 230150, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107687}, {"id": 223751, "content": "只会瞪眼的不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028046}, {"id": 224007, "content": "   我认为  看演员表现一些情绪时他的面部表情是否自然而生动，不然人觉得很尬。也就是有层次。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083919}, {"id": 265736, "content": "配音不行 眼睛要有戏 演开心不能演成缺心眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265150}, {"id": 224008, "content": "不像演出来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388018}, {"id": 223753, "content": "只记得角色名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171613}, {"id": 223754, "content": "能让你感同身受吧，不管是他的开心，还是愤怒，还是痛苦，都让你觉得这是很自然的一个人伤心时的表达，引起共鸣吧。表情，声音，肢体语言都很重要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034369}, {"id": 224010, "content": "古尔丹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732292}, {"id": 223755, "content": "可以从每一帧看出这个演员的表达，每一帧都没有浪费。开始就被电影磨练的演员，演技都是不错的。窦骁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034369}, {"id": 224779, "content": "10秒内流泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076842}, {"id": 223756, "content": "现在的演技我已经看不出来了，除了有些老配角之外，其他怎么老感觉差不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988152}, {"id": 229644, "content": "演员名单上有杨天宝 李易峰 陈学冬 杨洋等名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465848}, {"id": 223757, "content": "对于情景变化的反应。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902112}, {"id": 224013, "content": "眼神，面部表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 223758, "content": "小鲜肉=弃剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789122}, {"id": 224014, "content": "观看演员演的一些反差类的角色，如逗逼鱼高冷，好人与大反派，再从他的细节入手，特别是哭戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083940}, {"id": 224270, "content": "是不是我对象的新男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080366}, {"id": 223759, "content": "妖娆的小鲜肉。和，妩媚的男生", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999123}, {"id": 224015, "content": "赵丽颖不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076400}, {"id": 223760, "content": "把陈词滥调大众演法翻新让人忍不住看好几遍揣摩 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813084}, {"id": 224784, "content": "永远在瞪眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088226}, {"id": 223761, "content": "演什么，像什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814422}, {"id": 224018, "content": "原声的台词功底+每一个细节+情绪变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824469}, {"id": 224786, "content": "干嚎没眼泪，配音太过，演员太浅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920530}, {"id": 224019, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815318}, {"id": 224787, "content": "目前国内还能看的几个当红，都是琼瑶剧培训出来的，还珠三刘涛、马伊琍、秦岚、勉强黄晓明算一个，花非花雾非雾杨紫、邓伦……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920530}, {"id": 223764, "content": "我喜欢看这个演员嘴巴的戏多不多 比如害羞时候的舔嘴 嘴角的邪笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083443}, {"id": 224020, "content": "看妆面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542691}, {"id": 223765, "content": "念台词咬字准确\n眼神抓人\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112307}, {"id": 224021, "content": "看到这个人的演技，我想到的是这个演员还是这个角色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169549}, {"id": 224533, "content": "因为角色记住演员  而不是演员记住角色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957763}, {"id": 223766, "content": "杜绝死鱼脸是基本准则！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126942}, {"id": 224022, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573173}, {"id": 224023, "content": "不走心的不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473398}]}